      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. WILL (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with two wins and two minors from six tries. Placed last time (24.51) at Sale in a Free For All, finishing second and beaten a head. With a clean break looks hard to beat. ULTIMATE WARRIOR (7) was below best at his last start when 7th at The Meadows following a win (30.21) there two back. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Better than last start and can bounce back. GIACOMO (6) goes very well this course and distance starting 18 times for eight wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (30.54) when third at The Meadows in a Grade 5. Looks a key chance on best figures. ZIPPING SIGRID (2) has been in the frame at her last two runs, most recently when third (30.53) in a Grade 5 over 525m at The Meadows.",
